      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a solid start. let's dive into the \"dress codes\" part first. if someone wants to look \"universally professional\" or high-end, what are the core standards or baseline clothes they should aim for? basically, what's the foundation of looking sophisticated in a global business setting?",
